=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攞來衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmolamola</blockquote><br />\n教會幫過呀媽所以佢入咗教 但係佢個心係偏信道教果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀媽將我個電話開心share咗係佢個教會gp到"},{"pid":"200037f320a56ecb1e47dbdc445c82163255779a","tid":141413,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:12:38.000Z","msg":"加油爸打"},{"pid":"6ab69e76ecc3f061aabba1a4fae03b97130a54e5","tid":141413,"uid":33471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年九月尾出cert 依家三月 過咗五個月左右<br />\n呀媽一直都話好擔心我 成日同教會班人話我係屋企唔肯去搵野做<br />\n但事實係搵極都無人請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Send親CV都好似石沈大海咁<br />\n之後尋日教會有條友就send咗條講社工點救隱青出苦海嘅link比佢<br />\n佢特燈拎比我睇 嗰下真係好唔開心好想喊<br />\n然後教會班人又whatsapp我 叫我去做下義補幫下社會<br />\n我心諗依家你明知我咁嘅狀況仲叫我去做義工係咪混吉？<br />\n<br />\n我就快痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比呀媽當係隱青都算 <br />\n教會班友真係正仆街係到落井下石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n16ugrad<br />\n上個月先返工路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工個大佬問我點解咁遲<br />\n係佢口中覺得應該會有親戚朋友老師介紹到工俾後生仔<br />\n<br />\n事實就係cv石沉大海<br />\n<br />\n而兩位長老就覺得搵工係好似幾十年前咁睇報紙 有電話就主動打去即約到面試咁<br />\n只係上網取代左報紙"},{"pid":"d89b22cdd259086fc1e7617bf49e3b03a35289e4","tid":141413,"uid":11717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"咪做下隱青先囉<br />\n返左工之後無得他他條過架啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：廢青"},{"pid":"bfe97f3c7b7d2b4fa2a6d7425d5f0cf23310c018","tid":141413,"uid":54563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:14:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫你去做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/