.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係果句 傻閪先會信耶教/番教會<br />\n信得個腦都係閪迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你返工佢地咪冇錢收囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>返工佢地咪冇錢收囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bccd2be1b149cf552b46c3800c0c54f099563e","tid":141413,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教會+社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無敵組合，祝樓主好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf7f66c21e91128a1ade54bbc657022bf1ea292","tid":141413,"uid":54563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫你去做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死</blockquote><br />\n其實佢暗地裡同我呀媽講埋啲咩我都唔多想理<br />\n但係我失業仲叫我做義工...教會班人個腦係咪生草？？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔係咁講<br />\n你Send CV出去除咗send同in嗰陣其餘時間都係齋等架啦<br />\n佢地應該係擔心你成日將全副精神齋搵工會好易諗埋一邊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 你讀咩 我都16grad 上年8月先hea搵, 返咗半年工</blockquote><br />\n佢地唔知我搵緊工 係佢地眼中我只係一個隱青<br />\nasso 讀邊科唔講喇 得三十幾個人驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好羨慕絲打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9941d90aa226991a5707e84fa670a680d9e2ab08","tid":141413,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你屋企全家信教？<br />\n如果唔係<br />\n畀佢攞到你同你老母whatsapp&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n都幾失敗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攞來衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmolamola</blockquote><br />\n教會幫過呀媽所以佢入咗教 但係佢個心係偏信道教果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀媽將我個電話開心share咗係佢個教會gp到</blockquote><br />\nblock"},{"pid":"d7efc45a5a12ca1a4e98aa354dff59aa1c30d34d","tid":141413,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"其實佢唔係鬧你&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n或者畀說話你聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係擔心你嘅話<br />\n咁咪由佢擔心囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時你搵到工喇<br />\n咪當驚喜咁宣佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac19bef938d49e00b9c8ca5e174555b3f773159","tid":141413,"uid":4095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:26:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫你去做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死</blockquote><br />\n其實佢暗地裡同我呀媽講埋啲咩我都唔多想理<br />\n但係我失業仲叫我做義工...教會班人個腦係咪生草？？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔係咁講<br />\n你Send CV出去除咗send同in嗰陣其餘時間都係齋等架啦<br />\n佢地應該係擔心你成日將全副精神齋搵工會好易諗埋一邊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 你讀咩 我都16grad 上年8月先hea搵, 返咗半年工</blockquote><br />\n佢地唔知我搵緊工 係佢地眼中我只係一個隱青<br />\nasso 讀邊科唔講喇 得三十幾個人驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好羨慕絲打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點解唔話佢地知你搵緊工, 咁樣會擔心你好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接D同佢地講話你其實有目標啦, 因為早排年尾又新年冇乜人會辭職job ad都少D, 搵唔到唔一定係你問題<br />\n<br />\nBTW 空白期如果你同interviewer講你有做義工唔係日日HEA喺屋企可能對你見工仲有幫助"},{"pid":"3ed7ef5c21ff58a72b7602364637ba7c8238e8e0","tid":141413,"uid":54563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:33:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫你去做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死</blockquote><br />\n其實佢暗地裡同我呀媽講埋啲咩我都唔多想理<br />\n但係我失業仲叫我做義工...教會班人個腦係咪生草？？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔係咁講<br />\n你Send CV出去除咗send同in嗰陣其餘時間都係齋等架啦<br />\n佢地應該係擔心你成日將全副精神齋搵工會好易諗埋一邊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 你讀咩 我都16grad 上年8月先hea搵, 返咗半年工</blockquote><br />\n佢地唔知我搵緊工 係佢地眼中我只係一個隱青<br />\nasso 讀邊科唔講喇 得三十幾個人驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好羨慕絲打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點解唔話佢地知你搵緊工, 咁樣會擔心你好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接D同佢地講話你其實有目標啦, 因為早排年尾又新年冇乜人會辭職job ad都少D, 搵唔到唔一定係你問題<br />\n<br />\nBTW 空白期如果你同interviewer講你有做義工唔係日日HEA喺屋企可能對你見工仲有幫助</blockquote><br />\n之前有講過 但係呀媽見我差唔多日日都係屋企所以唔信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就同教會班人大肆宣揚我唔肯搵工日日匿係屋企<br />\n再之後就係上面打嘅野...<br />\n<br />\n義工真係有用？我一直覺得佢同中學課外活動差唔多level<br />\n但係依個教會我無咩好感 唔想同佢地有瓜葛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7d224da841f652b62408b9866872379498766e","tid":141413,"uid":28538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>教會+社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無敵組合，祝樓主好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 駁唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心覺得呢個組合既人   講果d所謂道理都好 un耳</blockquote><br />\n個啲係撚道理"},{"pid":"abe75b137a625650bda8fd0f86a228285efd1d48","tid":141413,"uid":4095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫你去做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死</blockquote><br />\n其實佢暗地裡同我呀媽講埋啲咩我都唔多想理<br />\n但係我失業仲叫我做義工...教會班人個腦係咪生草？？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔係咁講<br />\n你Send CV出去除咗send同in嗰陣其餘時間都係齋等架啦<br />\n佢地應該係擔心你成日將全副精神齋搵工會好易諗埋一邊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 你讀咩 我都16grad 上年8月先hea搵, 返咗半年工</blockquote><br />\n佢地唔知我搵緊工 係佢地眼中我只係一個隱青<br />\nasso 讀邊科唔講喇 得三十幾個人驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好羨慕絲打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點解唔話佢地知你搵緊工, 咁樣會擔心你好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接D同佢地講話你其實有目標啦, 因為早排年尾又新年冇乜人會辭職job ad都少D, 搵唔到唔一定係你問題<br />\n<br />\nBTW 空白期如果你同interviewer講你有做義工唔係日日HEA喺屋企可能對你見工仲有幫助</blockquote><br />\n之前有講過 但係呀媽見我差唔多日日都係屋企所以唔信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就同教會班人大肆宣揚我唔肯搵工日日匿係屋企<br />\n再之後就係上面打嘅野...<br />\n<br />\n義工真係有用？我一直覺得佢同中學課外活動差唔多level<br />\n但係依個教會我無咩好感 唔想同佢地有瓜葛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話做義工一定有用但總比同interviewer講你日日喺屋企有用<br />\n最忌就係俾位佢入話你唔主動, 俾你係閪人HR你都揀個有返PT/做義工嘅人啦, 睇落唔會係懶先吖嘛<br />\n做義工唔一定要返教會做嘅, 同你老母講清楚話你冇興趣返去, 而且有SEND CV只係未有回音<br />\n同埋有冇check過係咪cv有問題所以直接冇得IN?<br />\n<br />\n最後祝你早日搵到工唔使俾人煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a6406810c00de63471d05b8dcbe6278465b4a4","tid":141413,"uid":54563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫你去做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死</blockquote><br />\n其實佢暗地裡同我呀媽講埋啲咩我都唔多想理<br />\n但係我失業仲叫我做義工...教會班人個腦係咪生草？？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔係咁講<br />\n你Send CV出去除咗send同in嗰陣其餘時間都係齋等架啦<br />\n佢地應該係擔心你成日將全副精神齋搵工會好易諗埋一邊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 你讀咩 我都16grad 上年8月先hea搵, 返咗半年工</blockquote><br />\n佢地唔知我搵緊工 係佢地眼中我只係一個隱青<br />\nasso 讀邊科唔講喇 得三十幾個人驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好羨慕絲打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點解唔話佢地知你搵緊工, 咁樣會擔心你好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接D同佢地講話你其實有目標啦, 因為早排年尾又新年冇乜人會辭職job ad都少D, 搵唔到唔一定係你問題<br />\n<br />\nBTW 空白期如果你同interviewer講你有做義工唔係日日HEA喺屋企可能對你見工仲有幫助</blockquote><br />\n之前有講過 但係呀媽見我差唔多日日都係屋企所以唔信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就同教會班人大肆宣揚我唔肯搵工日日匿係屋企<br />\n再之後就係上面打嘅野...<br />\n<br />\n義工真係有用？我一直覺得佢同中學課外活動差唔多level<br />\n但係依個教會我無咩好感 唔想同佢地有瓜葛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話做義工一定有用但總比同interviewer講你日日喺屋企有用<br />\n最忌就係俾位佢入話你唔主動, 俾你係閪人HR你都揀個有返PT/做義工嘅人啦, 睇落唔會係懶先吖嘛<br />\n做義工唔一定要返教會做嘅, 同你老母講清楚話你冇興趣返去, 而且有SEND CV只係未有回音<br />\n同埋有冇check過係咪cv有問題所以直接冇得IN?<br />\n<br />\n最後祝你早日搵到工唔使俾人煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前一直都係搵ft 依家會搵住pt先<br />\n有時候講到明唔想去都係會比人好似傳銷咁話去教會試下先<br />\n放棄咗同佢地溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCV應該正常 以前比tutor執過 可能係我個人問題姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝絲打你聽我係到廢up...連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b1053ce81cccf67472a07483fd1b8b661e6cb6","tid":141413,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:56:53.000Z","msg":"俾老母小咗幾個月，去咗做萬寧，尋日第一日落鋪，做住先，唉"},{"pid":"8365b2382430a6b7927a5a49886ad4153e59f5e4","tid":141413,"uid":1059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上年九月尾出cert 依家三月 過咗五個月左右<br />\n呀媽一直都話好擔心我 成日同教會班人話我係屋企唔肯去搵野做<br />\n但事實係搵極都無人請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Send親CV都好似石沈大海咁<br />\n之後尋日教會有條友就send咗條講社工點救隱青出苦海嘅link比佢<br />\n佢特燈拎比我睇 嗰下真係好唔開心好想喊<br />\n然後教會班人又whatsapp我 叫我去做下義補幫下社會<br />\n我心諗依家你明知我咁嘅狀況仲叫我去做義工係咪混吉？<br />\n<br />\n我就快痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比呀媽當係隱青都算 <br />\n教會班友真係正仆街係到落井下石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\"